  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a non-stick pan over medium heat.",
    "Add ginger and scallions, sauté for about 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Stir in white chocolate, tamarind paste, soy sauce, and sugar. Stir well to combine all ingredients.",
